from pyspark.sql.functions import *

source_storageaccount_name = "datalakegzac4dn"
source_container_name = "eventhub"
source_relative_path = "dataeng/dataeng/*"

inputPath = 'abfss://%s@%s.dfs.core.windows.net/%s' % (source_container_name, source_storageaccount_name, source_relative_path)

inputStreamDf = spark.read.format('avro').load(inputPath)

inputStreamDf.printSchema

display(inputStreamDf)

#Transform data 
inputStreamDf = inputStreamDf.withColumn("Body", expr("CAST(Body as String)"))
inputStreamDf = inputStreamDf.select(inputStreamDf.Body, inputStreamDf.EnqueuedTimeUtc, inputStreamDf.Year, inputStreamDf.Month, inputStreamDf.Day)
#inputStreamDf = inputStreamDf.withColumnRenamed("Properties[MESSAGE_TYPE].member2", "MessageType")
display(inputStreamDf)

#Write out to data lake


target_storageaccount_name = "datalakegzac4dn"
target_container_name = "output"
target_relative_path = "Raw/EventHub"

target_path = 'abfss://%s@%s.dfs.core.windows.net/%s' % (target_container_name, target_storageaccount_name, target_relative_path)

inputStreamDf.write.partitionBy("Year", "Month", "Day").format("parquet").mode("overwrite").save(target_path)

#inputStreamDf.coalesce(1).write.partitionBy("MessageType", "Year", "Month", "Day").format("parquet").mode("overwrite").save(target_folder_path)
